@startuml
title Arquitetura em Camadas (Simplificada)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 120

package "Presentation Layer" as P {
  [Controllers]
  [Routes]
}

package "Application Layer" as A {
  [Use Cases / Services]
}

package "Domain Layer" as D {
  [Entities / Value Objects]
  [Domain Roles]
  [Repository Interfaces]
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" as I {
  [Repository Implementations]
  [PostgreSQL]
  [Auth (JWT/Bcrypt)]
  [Logging/Rate Limit]
}

P --> A : calls
A --> D : uses
D ..> I : ports implemented by
I --> D : implements interfaces

@enduml
